<ProjectDet
  title="Ani Web App"
  tech="UX UI | WEB APP"
  descript1="Astro | Tailwind CSS | Typescript"
  descript2="The Ani Web App is a comprehensive platform designed to provide users with a seamless experience in exploring and engaging with anime content. It features an intuitive interface, advanced search capabilities, and personalized recommendations, making it easy for users to discover new shows and connect with the anime community. The app is built with Astro for a fast, modern web experience and styled with Tailwind CSS for a responsive, component-driven design."
